dying for a drink.

25:16.616 --> 25:19.183
So she takes me
to a bar,

25:19.185 --> 25:20.851
and she gives me
to a waitress

25:20.853 --> 25:22.520
for a bucket of beer.

25:23.589 --> 25:25.256
