two days to file,
-(PHONE RINGING)

36:23.182 --> 36:24.314
so we should call
his people...

36:24.316 --> 36:26.850
WOMAN: Mr. Karn,
it's Mr. Manson again.

36:32.257 --> 36:33.990
Mr. Manson.

36:39.598 --> 36:41.131
Mr. Manson,
I am so sorry.

36:41.133 --> 36:43.166
I couldn't reach him.
May I take a message?

36:43.168 --> 36:45.302
May you take
my message?

36:45.304 --> 36:46.436
In return for what?

36:46.438 --> 36:49.940
Or do you just take
and take and take?

36:51.977 --> 36:53.043
I'm not sure.

36:53.045 --> 36:54.477
I'll let him know
that you called.

36:54.479 --> 36:56.546
What is the best number
to reach you?

36:56.815 --> 36:58.949
Sister Lady Cool Voice,

36:59.251 --> 37:01.518
I will reach him.

37:26.878 --> 37:29.279
Ah, on the clock.

37:29.815 --> 37:33.283
I don't remember you
being so rule-abiding.

37:33.285 --> 37:35.185
Live and learn.

37:40.626 --> 37:42.125
So this guy...

37:42.127 --> 37:45.362
You seen him maybe
just hanging around?

37:46.098 --> 37:48.131
Name Manson ring a bell?

37:51.603 --> 37:53.770
Your husband
was his lawyer.

37:55.140 --> 37:55.438
What?

37:55.440 --> 37:58.174
I don't think this is about
Manson and your daughter.

37:59.678 --> 38:02.212
It's about Manson
and your husband.

38:24.269 --> 38:26.069
MANSON: Hey, Ken.

38:27.005 --> 38:28.405
(EXHALES)

38:28.473 --> 38:30.173
Charlie...

38:31.543 --> 38:32.976
Been callin'.

38:33.912 --> 38:34.978
I know.

38:34.980 --> 38:38.481
Got out,
left messages a bunch.

38:38.483 --> 38:40.116
And it's got to stop.

38:40.118 --> 38:42.585
I like your cool voice
little miss secretary

38:42.587 --> 38:44.821
you got answering
your phone.

38:45.190 --> 38:47.324
I'll bet she's a tight
little mink.

38:47.326 --> 38:52.362
(LAUGHS) And you want
everyone to think
you're doin' her, right?

38:52.831 --> 38:55.198
'Cause boys will be boys.

38:58.403 --> 39:00.437
You and me know that.

39:02.040 --> 39:03.039
Back in the day,

39:03.041 --> 39:05.942
I couldn't round the
whores up fast enough

39:05.944 --> 39:07.377
for all your big swinging,

39:07.379 --> 39:10.747
lead pipe stud buddies,
remember?

39:11.516 --> 39:13.383
I remember everything,

39:13.552 --> 39:16.019
good times, bad times...

39:16.021 --> 39:17.454
KEN: Listen.

39:17.456 --> 39:19.723
I did what I could for you.

39:20.525 --> 39:22.025
I'm sorry, okay?

39:22.027 --> 39:22.592
Stay away from me.

39:22.594 --> 39:26.329
All I need is to meet
some folks you maybe know

39:26.331 --> 39:27.897
in the music biz.

39:27.899 --> 39:30.367
'Cause that's where
I'm fully at now, man,

39:30.369 --> 39:33.470
bringing the world my message,
my music.

39:35.240 --> 39:37.507
You remember
my songs, Kenny?

39:38.176 --> 39:40.510
Pretty sure I sang you a few.

39:47.686 --> 39:49.018
Okay.

39:49.988 --> 39:53.323
You don't want to help
your old friend Charlie,

39:53.392 --> 39:56.526
I'll just slink off,
go home...

39:56.528 --> 39:58.428
(KEYS JINGLING)

39:59.698 --> 40:01.264
(SIGHS)

40:01.833 --> 40:05.402
Tell my little girl
all my problems.

40:05.537 --> 40:09.973
Yeah, she's sweet,
that little Emma.

40:11.543 --> 40:13.009
She's with you?

40:15.280 --> 40:17.981
You want to know
what it sounds like?

40:18.150 --> 40:19.783
(MOANING)

40:23.288 --> 40:25.088
(GRUNTS)

40:25.791 --> 40:26.756
(KEN GASPS)

40:26.758 --> 40:28.558
There's a good daddy.

40:30.061 --> 40:31.461
(GASPS)

40:32.164 --> 40:33.630
Shh.

40:34.833 --> 40:36.266
I know.

40:36.835 --> 40:37.634
I know.

40:37.636 --> 40:40.703
Don't... Charlie, don't...

40:43.008 --> 40:45.275
Charlie, don't...

40:45.277 --> 40:49.712
Did I ever tell you
about the first time?

40:49.981 --> 40:51.381
Just like this...

40:51.383 --> 40:52.782
(GROANS)

40:53.118 --> 40:54.517
Back in juvie,

40:54.519 --> 40:56.719
sweet little crying thang.

40:57.522 --> 40:59.189
(TIRES SCREECHING)

41:04.963 --> 41:06.596
(SOBBING)

41:12.337 --> 41:14.471
That was a mood killer.

41:17.209 --> 41:20.477
Anyway, I gotta get.

41:21.279 --> 41:23.213
(MUMBLING)

41:28.253 --> 41:30.453
(CHUCKLES)

41:33.124 --> 41:34.757
You don't mind, do you?

41:34.759 --> 41:36.793
Your little girl's hungry.

41:37.562 --> 41:38.995
So, hey,

41:39.598 --> 41:41.731
let's get together again.

41:41.867 --> 41:45.034
Maybe next time
I'll bring your daughter,

41:45.036 --> 41:48.137
and the three of us
can get freaky-deaky.

41:59.985 --> 42:01.150
(SOBS)
